@startuml
!include _style.puml

title 前端交互：研报选股下拉组件状态图

state "Idle\n(未聚焦)" as Idle
state "Open\n(展开)" as Open
state "Loading\n(请求中)" as Loading
state "Error\n(请求失败)" as Error
state "Ready\n(有结果)" as Ready

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Open : focus / input change
Open --> Loading : 输入非空且触发查询
Loading --> Ready : 请求成功且 results>0
Loading --> Open : 请求成功且 results=0
Loading --> Error : 请求失败/超时

Error --> Loading : 修改输入重试
Ready --> Loading : 修改输入继续搜索

Open --> Idle : 点击外部/ESC/取消
Ready --> Idle : 选中股票并关闭（当前实现）

note right of Ready
当前实现中：Enter 默认选中第一条搜索结果\n并关闭下拉
end note

@enduml
